📈 RFM Analysis
🧠 What is RFM Analysis?

RFM Analysis is a customer segmentation technique used to identify valuable customers based on:

🕒 Recency

How recently the customer made a purchase.

🔁 Frequency

How frequently the customer purchases products.

💰 Monetary

How much money the customer spends.

👥 Customer Segments
Segment	Description
🏆 Premium Customers	High value loyal customers
❤️ Loyal Customers	Frequent repeat buyers
📈 Potential Customers	Customers with growth potential
⚠️ At Risk Customers	Customers showing reduced activity
❌ Lost Customers	Inactive customers
